{"tid":1265441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[高級黑]抗爭之歌-義勇軍進行曲","createTime":"2019-06-29T07:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T08:32:30.000Z","uid":193565,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2d13175108732d95b5809a39163db8f367b68e6b","tid":1265441,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"經過今次事件，小弟終於明白國歌嘅神髓，作為愛國市民梗係要多d唱國歌啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國歌歷史：<br />\n1949年11月15日，《人民日報》發表了關於國旗、國歌和年號&ldquo;新華社答讀者問&rdquo;：&ldquo;《義勇軍進行曲》是十餘年來在中國廣大人民的鬥爭中最流行的歌曲，已經具有歷史意義。採用《義勇軍進行曲》為中華人民共和國現時的國歌而不加修改，是為了喚起人民回想祖國創造過程中的艱難憂患，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鼓舞人民發揚反抗帝國主義侵略的愛國熱情，把革命進行到底</span></span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%89%E5%8B%87%E5%86%9B%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B9%2589%25E5%258B%2587%25E5%2586%259B%25E8%25BF%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%259B%25B2&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq4dddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7a09d51a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B9%89%E5%8B%87%E5%86%9B%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n《義勇軍進行曲》<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">起來！不願做奴隸的人們！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/10/99/6411965.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1140\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2F99%2F6411965.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1140&h=2de134dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">把我們的血肉，築成我們新的長城！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uz62qJw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuz62qJw.jpg&h=c469eddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中華民族到了最危險的時候</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ib657P5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fib657P5.jpg&h=8ee35a30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">每個人被迫著發出最後的吼聲</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uoVKDW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuoVKDW9.jpg&h=2f3ec4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起來！<br />\n起來！<br />\n起來！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們萬眾一心，冒著敵人的砲火前進</span></span>！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dB2tmdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdB2tmdN.jpg&h=b2769657&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冒著敵人的砲火前進！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dswt5Eg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdswt5Eg.jpg&h=19294b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前進！<br />\n前進！進！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七一定要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抗爭定要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中小學一定要教唱國歌，最重要係國歌入面嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭精神</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛國愛港就要唱國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國歌法？支持港人學習抗爭精神</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲中小學老師教授國歌歷史</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c5971151b87b49ee12ef06722ab43881ac2f11","tid":1265441,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a69c171ed779fc3deb6d2f48f1cdf153a14ce87","tid":1265441,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"真係要做先得架<br />\n我琴晚煮飯個陣都想到呢首歌<br />\n幾時推翻呢個垃圾"},{"pid":"44c571014aabc36c2b5fcf59a04e95adcac75a1d","tid":1265441,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:55:16.000Z","msg":"唔得，頂唔順，想嘔"},{"pid":"8bf9959378b91bc59af523f7daaaa32338fce388","tid":1265441,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T07:58:41.000Z","msg":"國家俾咗咁大粒彈藥我地梗係要好好利用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec32fc1e4ded47be11211ca3ee781d921274f7a1","tid":1265441,"uid":88813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"除咗中華民族四個字，其他中曬"},{"pid":"dc035d3ddbac2559c6a852eb0df43aaa504c3e6f","tid":1265441,"uid":93236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec32fc1e4ded47be11211ca3ee781d921274f7a1","tid":1265441,"uid":88813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"除咗中華民族四個字，其他中曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-2